{"tid":1632091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住，雖然咁講前線一定唔鍾意，但希望你地明白","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:23.000Z","uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b846d67fa6d310d2f2d80691bc535a826d6b947c","tid":1632091,"uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢8月一出臥底果陣，係我地手足換番黎嘅好牌，所有破壞從此由黑警負責，只係之後又話唔好沉迷捉鬼，跟住就再無人將破壞歸究係臥底。<br />\n<br />\n我認同唔好沉迷捉鬼，但其實將咩L野都賴落黑警到最方便論述，尤其係呢家和勇開始被分化，賴哂落鬼到最方便。PS 討論邊啲行為acceptable 長遠都係必要，但呢家處理discourse 問題更緊要。"},{"pid":"a6a16b3f4ef08e45aa07001b2d74e8c5a2052274","tid":1632091,"uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"5ce5b68af1e4cc1c3147630ed95a7ebba20b9138","tid":1632091,"uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a10a704f26995e97b8688f2bc65454613452c03","tid":1632091,"uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"我推"},{"pid":"4b6fc81a3e0fe73c55057ed3283c52779010b89f","tid":1632091,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"可以賴, 但始終無實質既證據, 所以唔一定說服到人"},{"pid":"a026a5b543e2048f4d72f94524a228792d9e0327","tid":1632091,"uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"844ded7364a1ff7e432fe1a5fd8d1f0f443fb7b6","tid":1632091,"uid":291722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6fc81a3e0fe73c55057ed3283c52779010b89f","tid":1632091,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"可以賴, 但始終無實質既證據, 所以唔一定說服到人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"Solomon 信"},{"pid":"60d9742830ae281bce3445d138bbfb08c358cb91","tid":1632091,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"唔同意 <br />\n<br />\n唔好學